{"tid":513172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯案】前妻到庭拒回應上訴 藍絲翹手阻記者追訪","createTime":"2017-12-29T09:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T16:17:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"97482c6c7051563f0ef242f5a43c28c1c22473c8","tid":513172,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514537614_0105.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514537614_0105.png&h=10558a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱經緯前妻離開法庭時被大批傳媒追訪，她未有回應朱會否提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514537705_1a8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514537705_1a8e.png&h=7f536132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有多名朱的支持者散庭時手蹺手走在前排，遮擋準備離開的朱經緯家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514537061_d28f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514537061_d28f.png&h=096c04c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n混亂期間一名女子（紅圈示）聲稱被非禮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在佔旺期間因用警棍毆打途人的退休警司朱經緯，早前被法庭裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成，東區法院裁判官今日下午約2點半開會開庭作出判刑。裁判官開庭後表示，要考慮判刑因素，押後至下月3日判刑，被告須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n法院下午兩點半開庭，並安排76個公眾席讓市民進內聽取判決。大批「藍絲」在法院門口眾集並播放改編「男兒當自強」的撐警歌，有人一早到庭排隊輪籌入庭撐朱經緯，但有關座位將優先派發給傳媒記者，有公眾人士對安排不滿，不斷以以粗言辱罵司法機構做法不公，「CY案嗰陣都唔係咁」、「欺負中國人民呀！」<br />\n<br />\n當法庭決定押後判刑至下周三（1月3日），朱的家人離開法庭時，多名支持者手翹手走在前列遮擋。有傳媒發現朱太的蹤影即上前採訪，追問她會否為丈夫提出上訴，但她並無回應。由於在場有多間傳媒採訪，她一時無法登上私家車，支持者亦上前將她包圍阻擋傳媒採訪。期間有上了年紀的女性在人群中忽然大叫「非禮」，聲稱被人用手掃到其胸部，朱太則在混亂上登上私家車離開。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱被非禮的女子不斷叫囂，有其他支持者亦上前向記者惡言相向，多名警員趕到要求記者和支持者返回行人路。期間該名聲稱被非禮的女子繼續大聲批評「人嚟㗎嘛！你未見過人咩？你哋頭先隻手掂到我，你係做嘢定搞嘢？」旁邊的人亦喝罵記者「喂！你仲影？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57639320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57639320&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YveU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=51a3f8d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57639320&h=10e39612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57639320</a>"},{"pid":"d87930b159af4371e6f3e0ba9b2aacfa061a6d3b","tid":513172,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"a9dde9e225d34bcc6b425f997085abc87cd6624e","tid":513172,"uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"阿嬋: #metoo"},{"pid":"c3d3060d97386613837654c0afd00400de869727","tid":513172,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"仲還押緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0981d0d59c01f3d8e771e53eefb9367eaa63667c","tid":513172,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edeaf397a2c4a9927512f7497a5492fdea4f84d","tid":513172,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9dde9e225d34bcc6b425f997085abc87cd6624e","tid":513172,"uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"阿嬋: #metoo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"考慮報警未？"},{"pid":"fc54a0af867408a2d5c4ebced3a748117a70cc7d","tid":513172,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"煎pan是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c533cedeee4627f551cc41745ceac2674a7442","tid":513172,"uid":2436,"like":11,"dislike"