edaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57639320</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係被打嗰個先係真正中國人民喎， 個受害人係大陸出世， 無人話佢哋知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}